title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1994-10-14
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, West L.A. Fadeaway, Queen Jane Approximately, Lazy River Road, El Paso*, Ramble On Rose, Box Of Rain

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Looks Like Rain, Samba In The Rain, Corinna-> Drums-> Space-> I Need A Miracle-> Attics Of My Life-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Liberty

*Weir on acoustic guitar

reviews.review_text:
Best of the Audience recordings! This one is the best of the audience recordings, with clear notes and very little of the boominess that is so frequent in non-SBD sound. The vocals are also clear. Check it out, play a bit of several songs...I've checked all the AUD shows and this one definitely is a step above the others.

The musical item most of you would be looking for is the over 30-minute version of Scarlet > Fire, and it's good here. But some of the other songs are also good: Lazy River Road, Attics of my Life, etc. Thanks, Charlie Miller & co., for uploading this!
